de.mrapp.android.adapter.expandablelist.selectable

Interface ExpandableListSelectionListener<GroupType,ChildType>

  • Type Parameters:
    GroupType - The type of the underlying data of the observed adapter's group items
    ChildType - The type of the underlying data of the observed adapter's child items

    public interface ExpandableListSelectionListener<GroupType,ChildType>
    Defines the interface, all listeners, which should be notified when the selection of a group or child item of a ExpandableListAdapter has been modified, must implement.
    Since:
    0.1.0
